                    <div class="content-card border-l-4 border-teal-500">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Blended VM + RVM Kiosk</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">We integrate a traditional Vending Machine (VM) with a Reverse Vending Machine (RVM) into a single, smart kiosk. This kiosk serves both commercial and recycling functions, making it financially sustainable from Day 1.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Internal DRS - Removed ** from around the fee -->
                    <div class="content-card border-l-4 border-teal-500">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Creating an Internal DRS Loop</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">We pioneer India's first internal DRS by adding a voluntary ₹2-₹3 fee to our own products. This exact fee is fully refunded upon recycling, creating an instant, self-funded consumer incentive loop for our specific bottles.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- New PDF Link Button - Updated text -->
