                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Convincing the Stakeholders</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">We use the auditable data generated in Phase 1 to lobby the Government and major Beverage Companies (like Coca-Cola and PepsiCo) to adopt a formal national DRS policy, transferring responsibility for the deposit and refund funds to them.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-card bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Dedicated RVM Rollout</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Once the national policy is in place, we shift our focus entirely to high-volume RVMs in busy stations, malls, and shops, accepting all plastic bottles and tins that fall under the new national DRS framework.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
